{"tid":1165444,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［多圖］一個人坐三日火車跨越美國","createTime":"2019-05-21T19:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T09:52:15.000Z","uid":177973,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"61e47eab8358ba6f3e9ef5e170108c219d282d16","tid":1165444,"uid":177973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:43:12.000Z","msg":"又係我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說唔寫比利時遊記都唔發現<br />\n原來連登咁多人睇遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當堂令我有種衝動想share返上年坐三日火車跨越美國單嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都一年前 細節廢事寫太多<br />\n大家當睇下Amtrak review同睇下相算啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vbnSQZJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvbnSQZJ.png&h=7de9d7a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（上年仲用緊fujifilm XT20 <br />\n相味精有啲多大家將就一下）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nBkfru.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nBkfru.png&h=5b9cbcdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說我坐個條線叫加洲微風號 (California Zephyr)<br />\n係美鐵Amtrak數一數二嘅觀光路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLiterally跨越美國 全長3690公里<br />\n會經過沙漠雪山河川麥田城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事源我上年去咗LA summer exchange <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又想去east coast睇musical<br />\n本身份人又鍾意火車(好鍾意睇Before sunrise<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n所以就單人匹馬買車飛 <br />\n由頭坐到尾坐足三日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/088VOOw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F088VOOw.png&h=94ae99df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路線係由San Francisco坐到去Chicago<br />\n由於無錢(again)<br />\n所以我係坐座位 而坐座位嘅窮L係唔配有浴室沖涼 所以我三日都無沖過涼 痕到仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vTyAuf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vTyAuf.png&h=cd670b20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZuU4nL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZuU4nL.png&h=2bfc09d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wef1KnT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWef1KnT.png&h=7425b2bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkeFfuA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkeFfuA.png&h=dbc26256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過火車上其實好多人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且火車有觀光車廂同餐廳車廂<br />\n所以都有好多空間俾乘客走動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9UR8poA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9UR8poA.png&h=eb4be404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年係火車日日同其他乘客講英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係英文突飛猛進<br />\n之後再分享乘客趣事！"},{"pid":"20dab796d332394785adcc29a63f936aa9400703","tid":1165444,"uid":177973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:47:40.000Z","msg":"以下係風景相精華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三日唯一做嘅就係影相同傾計<br />\n所以仲有好多相就唔po啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7RNSQ4R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7RNSQ4R.png&h=85e88750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZjJXK0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZjJXK0.png&h=77ad0561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVP9Tio.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVP9Tio.png&h=31ea4ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GuCjv46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGuCjv46.png&h=9522bb27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qc9mKp8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqc9mKp8.png&h=3e6bf885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uif88RR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuif88RR.png&h=aacc8d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KRMXhLc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRMXhLc.png&h=87376b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i0AX2bU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0AX2bU.png&h=673fe0fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ghph2bV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhph2bV.png&h=1b201f2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96576429ff26b2fd94b532a2dae4c4110a5f417d","tid":1165444,"uid":25960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:50:04.000Z","msg":"On<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08511fcdd6ac251c1bc7ab560bad77a40982b79","tid":1165444,"uid":177973,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:50:24.000Z","msg":"最得意係經過咗一個大campsite<br />\n入面有個傳統係一有火車經過<br />\n不論男女都會除褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後乘客就會好enjoy睇同船男人望住女人除褲嘅尷尬樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yA6PTjJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyA6PTjJ.png&h=4e440500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rnJKHc5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrnJKHc5.png&h=dda47bd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7777a71d7d825bf972e1818263cf3e426a0f4eda","tid":1165444,"