":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae57270bcd12d9c616567488eb39c7adf48b001e","tid":1165444,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T21:21:53.000Z","msg":"廁所會唔會好嘔心?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:58:49.000Z","msg":"唔會啊 好似飛機廁所咁"},{"pid":"af343dec410f02ef5661594aeca734c1d3aa79ff","tid":1165444,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:35:49.000Z","msg":"會唔會比人打劫"},{"pid":"6047b650cf7ee19e99e4e4895f52d065c7a4831f","tid":1165444,"uid":177973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af343dec410f02ef5661594aeca734c1d3aa79ff","tid":1165444,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:35:49.000Z","msg":"會唔會比人打劫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"我搭個次班車delay咗六個鐘<br />\n聽其他乘客講係因為有人take drug<br />\n之後被人告發 班車就停咗等警察嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後又有人心臟病發 於是又停咗等白車<br />\n<br />\n不過兩次我都見唔到有事發生<br />\n只係道聽途說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一日旁邊坐咗個好似homeless嘅人<br />\n帶住勁多臭菜同一樽泥色水<br />\n我勁驚 但佢之後主動同職員講調位<br />\n之後我都留意到佢剩係瞓觀光車廂<br />\n唔返位<br />\n<br />\n老實說 其實我都幾唔想同佢坐<br />\n佢眼神好creepy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋其實好多時候車無咩人可以一人坐兩個位當床瞓 方便好多 出入又唔洗叫人借過<br />\n所以當時都好慶幸佢自己調位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}